  "texts": [
    "Overall, we can see that adding predicted or gold salient entities to the model significantly improves the factuality of generated summaries and reduces hallucinations (lower scores are better), compare e.g.",
    "the total scores of the CTRL0 (0.737), CTRLPred (0.658) and CTRLGold models (0.537).",
    "Among all models, GPTPred produces summaries with the best entailment score (0.222).",
    "This demonstrates that adding predicted entities to GPT-4 contributes the most to improving faithfulness.",
